OL,3,CSenedd Election results due to be
OL,4,Cannounced as counting begins
OL,6,FCounts open from 9am in the 2026
OL,7,FSenedd Election after voters across
OL,8,FWales cast their ballots in what could
OL,9,Fprove to be one of the most
OL,10,Fsignificant elections in the nation's
OL,11,Fpolitical history.
OL,13,FPolling stations closed at 10pm on
OL,14,FThursday 7 May, with sealed ballot
OL,15,Fboxes now arriving at counting centres
OL,16,Facross Wales ahead of counting.
OL,18,FUnlike some previous elections, votes
OL,19,Fwere not counted overnight and will
OL,20,Finstead be calculated throughout
OL,21,FFriday 8 May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
