OL,3,CSenedd Election results due to be
OL,4,Cannounced as counting begins
OL,6,FThe first results are expected at
OL,7,Faround 2pm, with more due to be
OL,8,Fannounced throughout the afternoon.
OL,10,FThis year's election has seen a major
OL,11,Ftransformation in how the Senedd
OL,12,Foperates and how voters elect their
OL,13,Frepresentatives.
OL,15,FThe number of Members of the Senedd
OL,16,F(MSs) has increased from 60 to 96 in
OL,17,Fone of the biggest changes since
OL,18,Fdevolution began in 1999.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
