OL,3,CSenedd Election results due to be
OL,4,Cannounced as counting begins
OL,6,FWales has also been divided into 16
OL,7,Fnew super-constituencies, replacing
OL,8,Fthe previous 40.
OL,10,FEach constituency will elect six MSs
OL,11,Funder the proportional D'Hondt voting
OL,12,Fsystem, where even small shifts in
OL,13,Fvote share can significantly affect
OL,14,Fseat distribution.
OL,16,FToday's count will determine the 96
OL,17,Fpoliticians who will shape decisions
OL,18,Fon health, education, transport and
OL,19,Fother devolved issues over the next
OL,20,Ffour years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
